# Multiplication Table Challenge - COM214 Programming Assignment 3 - 3/31/26

## Project Overview
This project is an interactive web-based multiplication table game where users can test their multiplication skills. Users enter a table size (1-20), and a multiplication table is generated with one random cell left blank. The user must enter the correct product before a timer (equal to the table size in seconds) expires.

## Team Members & Roles

### Rebecca (Frontend Developer)
- Designed and implemented the HTML structure
- Created all CSS styling including:
  - Checkerboard pattern with animated color transitions
  - Responsive table design with uniform cell sizing
  - Animated border effect for the placeholder image
  - Centered layout and visual styling
- Ensured cross-browser compatibility
- Managed the visual presentation and user interface

### Josiah (Backend Developer)
- Implemented all JavaScript functionality including:
  - Input validation (1-20 range, numeric only)
  - Dynamic multiplication table generation
  - Random blank cell placement
  - Timer system with countdown functionality
  - Answer verification and feedback system
  - State management (table generation, reset, and cleanup)
  - Integration with existing HTML/CSS structure

